  "INDICATIVE EMBROIDERY ":"INDICATIVE EMBROIDERY ",
  "<p>All transactions related to the optional\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Protection Plan program are governed solely by the provisions of the applicable Agreement. This document and its contents provide general information about the\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Protection Plan program and should not be solely relied upon when purchasing coverage. Please refer to the applicable\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Protection Plan program Agreement for details of terms, conditions, and specific coverage details, including limitations and exclusions, transferability, and cancelability. Coverage may vary by state. Not all vehicle models may be eligible for coverage. Please see your Dealer for more information.</p>\r\n<p>The Administrator/Obligor of Tire &amp; Wheel Protection, Dent Protection, and Windshield Protection included in the\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Protection Plan program is Safe-Guard Products International, LLC, Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, +1 844 670 1876, except in Florida where the Administrator/ Obligor of Tire &amp; Wheel Protection and Dent Protection is Safe-Guard Warranty Corporation, Florida License Number 60126, Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, +1 844 670 1876.</p>\r\n<p>The Administrator of Guaranteed Auto Protection (GAP) included in the\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Protection Plan program is Safe-Guard Products International, LLC, Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, +1 844 670 1876, except in Indiana where the GAP Plan Administrator is Safe-Guard Warranty Corporation, Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, +1 844 670 1876.</p>\r\n<p>The Administrator of Lease-End Protection included in the\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Protection Plan program is Safe-Guard Products International, LLC, Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, +1 844 670 1876.</p>\r\n<p>Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars Financial Services<br />\r\nA division of BMW Financial Services NA, LLC</p>\r\n<p>5550 Britton Parkway, Hilliard, OH 43026<br />\r\nTel: 1-877-877-3735 Fax: 1-800-820-4269</p>\r\n<p>Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars NA, LLC, 300 Chesnut Ridge Road, Woodcliff Lake, NJ 07677-7731</p>\r\n<p>\u00a9 Copyright\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars NA, LLC, 2017. Not to be reproduced or transmitted. The\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0name and logo are registered trademarks owned by or licensed to\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars NA, LLC.</p>\r\n":"<p>옵션인\u00a0롤스로이스\u00a0Protection Plan 프로그램과 관련된 모든 거래는 해당 계약의 조항에 지배를 받습니다. 이 문서와 이 문서의 내용은\u00a0롤스로이스\u00a0Protection Plan 프로그램에 대한 전반적인 정보를 제공하나, 보장을 구매할 때 전적으로 이에 의존해서는 안됩니다. 제한 사항과 및 제외 사항, 양도 가능여부, 취소 가능여부를 포함하는 약관과 조건, 그리고 보장 범위에 대한 자세한 내용은 해당\u00a0롤스로이스\u00a0Protection Plan 프로그램 계약서를 참조하십시오. 보장 범위는 주마다 다를 수 있습니다. 모든 차량 모델이 보장 범위에 포함되지 않을 수 있습니다. 자세한 정보는 딜러에게 문의하십시오.</p>\r\n<p>\u00a0롤스로이스\u00a0Protection Plan 프로그램에 포함된 Tire &amp; Wheel Protection, Dent Protection, Windshield Protection의 관리/의무자는 Safe-Guard Products International, LLC이며, 주소는 Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, 전화번호는 +1 844 670 1876입니다. 플로리다는 예외적으로, Tire &amp; Wheel Protection과 Dent Protection의 관리/의무자는 Safe-Guard Warranty Corporation이며, 플로리다 면허 번호 60126, 주소는 Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, 전화번호는 +1 844 670 1876입니다.</p>\r\n<p>\u00a0롤스로이스\u00a0Protection Plan 프로그램에 포함된 Guaranteed Auto Protection(GAP)의 관리자는 Safe-Guard Products International, LLC이며, 주소는 Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, 전화번호는 +1 844 670 1876입니다. 인디아나는 예외적으로 GAP Plan 관리자는 Safe-Guard Warranty Corporation이며, 주소는 Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, 전화번호는 +1 844 670 1876입니다.</p>\r\n<p>\u00a0롤스로이스\u00a0Protection Plan 프로그램에 포함된 Lease-End Protection의 관리자는 Safe-Guard Products International, LLC이며, 주소는 Two Concourse Parkway, Suite 500, Atlanta, GA 30328, 전화번호는 +1 844 670 1876입니다.</p>\r\n<p>Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars Financial Services<br />\r\nA division of BMW Financial Services NA, LLC</p>\r\n<p>5550 Britton Parkway, Hilliard, OH 43026<br />\r\nTel: 1-877-877-3735 Fax: 1-800-820-4269</p>\r\n<p>Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars NA, LLC, 300 Chesnut Ridge Road, Woodcliff Lake, NJ 07677-7731</p>\r\n<p>\u00a9 Copyright\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars NA, LLC, 2017. 재생산 또는 전송 금지. \u00a0롤스로이스\u00a0명칭과 로고는\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars Limited의 고유 라이센스 상표입니다.</p>\r\n",
