  "<h4>NEDC (combined): CO2 emission: 371-366 g/km; Fuel consumption: 17.3-17.5 mpg / 16.3-16.1 l/100km.&nbsp;<a href=\"#emission\">*</a> WLTP (combined): CO2 emission: 384-367 g/km; Fuel consumption: 16.5-17.3 mpg / 17.1-16.3 l/100km&nbsp;<a href=\"#emission\">#</a></h4>\r\n":"<h4>NEDC (복합): CO2 배출량: 371-366 g/km; 연비: 17.3-17.5 mpg / 16.3-16.1 l/100km.&nbsp;<a href=\"#emission\">*</a> WLTP (복합): CO2 배출량: 384-367 g/km; 연비: 16.5-17.3 mpg / 17.1-16.3 l/100km&nbsp;<a href=\"#emission\">#</a></h4>\r\n",
