  "<h4><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">You can change your marketing preferences, withdraw your consent for marketing or object to our use of your data for marketing purposes by one of the following:<br />\r\n</span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Calling the Customer Contact Team on +44 (0)1243 525700</li>\r\n<br />\r\n<li>Sending an email to\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:enquiries@rolls-roycemotorcars.com\">enquiries@rolls-roycemotorcars.com</a></li>\r\n<br />\r\n<li>By writing to us at:<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Customer Contact Team<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars Limited<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The Drive<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Westhamptnett<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0West Sussex<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0England<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0PO18 0SH</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n":"<h4><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">아래 방법을 통해 마케팅 정보 수신 설정을 변경하거나, 마케팅 정보 수신 동의를 철회하거나, 마케팅 용도로 귀하의 개인 정보를 활용하는 것을 거부하실 수 있습니다.<br />\r\n</span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>고객 지원팀 전화 +44 (0)1243 525700</li>\r\n<br />\r\n<li>이메일\u00a0<a href=\"mailto:enquiries@rolls-roycemotorcars.com\">@rolls-roycemotorcars.com</a></li>\r\n<br />\r\n<li>우편:<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Customer Contact Team<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Rolls-Royce\u00a0Motor Cars Limited<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0The Drive<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0Westhamptnett<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0West Sussex<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0England<br />\r\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0PO18 0SH</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
