  "<h4>NEDCcorr (combined): CO2 emission: 343 g/km; Fuel consumption: 18.7 mpg / 15.1 l/100km\u00a0<a href=\"#emission\">*</a></h4>\r\n<h4>WLTP (combined): CO2 emission: 377-370 g/km; Fuel consumption: 17.0-17.3 mpg / 16.6-16.3 l/100km\u00a0<a href=\"#emission\">#</a></h4>\r\n":"<h4>NEDCcorr (복합): CO2 배출량: 343 g/km; 연비: 18.7 mpg / 15.1 l/100km\u00a0<a href=\"#emission\">*</a></h4>\r\n<h4>WLTP (복합): CO2 배출량: 377-370 g/km; 연비: 17.0-17.3 mpg / 16.6-16.3 l/100km\u00a0<a href=\"#emission\">#</a></h4>\r\n",
